null,{"className":"text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-teal pl-4","children":"Thinking about hiring a videographer but not sure where to start? Here's what to look for, what to ask, and how to make sure you get the right person for your project."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/[0.06] mb-10"}]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Whether you need coverage for a corporate event, a wedding, or a commercial project, hiring the right videographer can make or break the final product. The process can feel overwhelming if you've never done it before, but it doesn't have to be. Here's a straightforward breakdown of what to look for and how to approach it."]}],["$","h2","1",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Define Your Project First"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Before you start reaching out to anyone, get clear on what you actually need. Ask yourself:"]}],["$","ul","3",{"className":"list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"What is the purpose of the video? (Social media, internal training, broadcast, archive)"}],["$","li","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"How long does the final video need to be?"}],["$","li","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Where will it be shown?"}],["$","li","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"What's your budget?"}],["$","li","4",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"When do you need it?"}]]}],["$","p","4",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Having answers to these questions before you make contact will save you time and help the videographer give you an accurate quote."]}],["$","h2","5",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Look at Their Work, Not Just Their Website"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["A videographer's portfolio tells you more than any bio ever will. When reviewing their work, pay attention to:"]}],["$","p","7",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Consistency"}]," — Does the quality hold up across different projects, or does it look like one good piece surrounded by average work?"]}],["$","p","8",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Relevant experience"}]," — If you're hiring for a live event, look for examples of live event work. Wedding videographers and corporate videographers often have very different skill sets and shooting styles."]}],["$","p","9",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Audio quality"}]," — Bad audio ruins good video. Listen closely to the sound in their samples."]}],["$","p","10",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Editing style"}]," — Do they cut to the beat? Is the pacing appropriate for the subject matter? Editing is half the job."]}],["$","h2","11",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Understand What You're Paying For"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Videography rates vary widely depending on experience, equipment, location, and scope. On the Gulf Coast, day rates for experienced professionals typically range from a few hundred dollars for a half day to several thousand for a full production crew. What you're paying for includes:"]}],["$","ul","13",{"className":"list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Pre-production planning and communication"}],["$","li","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Shoot day hours and travel"}],["$","li","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Equipment — cameras, lenses, lighting, audio gear, stabilizers"}],["$","li","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Post-production editing and color correction"}],["$","li","4",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Revisions and delivery"}]]}],["$","p","14",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["A low quote isn't always a bargain. Make sure you understand exactly what's included before signing anything."]}],["$","h2","15",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Ask the Right Questions"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["When you make contact, a few questions will tell you a lot:"]}],["$","ul","17",{"className":"list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Do you have backup equipment on shoots?"}],["$","li","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Have you worked on projects similar to mine?"}],["$","li","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"What does your editing turnaround look like?"}],["$","li","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Do you offer raw footage?"}],["$","li","4",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"What happens if you get sick or have an emergency on the day?"}]]}],["$","p","18",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["A professional videographer will have clear, confident answers. If they hesitate on the backup equipment question, that's a red flag."]}],["$","h2","19",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Get It in Writing"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["No matter how casual the project feels, always have a written agreement before the shoot. A basic contract should cover the scope of work, payment terms, delivery timeline, what happens with revisions, and who owns the footage."]}],["$","p","21",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Hiring locally on the Gulf Coast has real advantages — someone who knows the area, understands the lighting conditions, and is available for a follow-up shoot if needed. Take the time to find the right fit and you'll end up with work you're proud of."]}]],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal/10 to-transparent border border-teal/20 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-3","children":"Find a Professional on the Gulf Coast"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-sm mb-6","children":"Browse verified media professionals available for your next project — from Tallahassee to New Orleans."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/browse","className":"btn-teal font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Browse Pros"}],["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/post-job","className":"btn-outline font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Post a Job"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-navy2 border-t border-white/[0.06] py-12 px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-6xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-displ